            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>宇隆(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2233:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2233\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2233-TW</a>)30日12:02上漲27元，股價漲停報300.0元，委買8張、委賣589張，成交4,360張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為精密金屬零件之機械加工、製造及買賣。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>宇隆(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2233:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2233\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2233-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲4.8%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲3.76%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+541 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+564 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-41 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+18 張</li> <li>融資增減：+482 張</li> <li>融券增減：+8 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
