            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>環球晶(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6488:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6488\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6488-TW</a>)30日11:58上漲53元，股價漲停報589.0元，委買27,000張，成交7,026張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為半導體晶棒及晶圓之研發、設計與製造。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>環球晶(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6488:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6488\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6488-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌10.67%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌3.12%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+580 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+2,674 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-1,461 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-633 張</li> <li>融資增減：+688 張</li> <li>融券增減：-76 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
